# CS488 A1
> Mingze Xu, #20806115
## Compilation
The compiation steps is as follows:
```{bash}
$ cd A1
$ premake4 gmake
$ make
$ ./A1
```
The dev program has been run on the local virtual machine

## Manual
- **Persistence module** will detect the state of your mouse upon release. If it remains
unmoved for a longer enough time (by default 2 frames) then the persistence will
not be triggered. If it is moving, then the speed upon release will be recorded
and used to set the rotation speed of persistence.
- **Scaling factor** is bounded by 0.5 and 2.0
- **Height of cube** is bounded by 1 and 10
